DataElement.preferredDefinition: Any record of a medical imaging event whether physical or electronic.:A written or verbal account, representation, statement, or explanation of something._The type of an expression with two possible values, "true" and "false". Also, a variable of Boolean type or a function with Boolean arguments or result. The most common Boolean functions are AND, OR and NOT.:Being or existing in a specified place or at the specified time._Values of two-valued logic.
